---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <fragment slot="header">
    <Header />
  </fragment>

  <Section>
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <span class="text-sm font-normal" style="color:#696969;">Audit de sécurité</span>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight" style="font-family: &quot;Futura Sd&quot;, Futura, &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 158, 224);">
        Votre entreprise est-elle vraiment protégée ?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm" style="color:#696969;">
        Test d'intrusion complet a 500 € HT. Rapport detaille en 48h.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5" style="background-color:#009EE0;">
        Je demande un audit
      </a>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight" style="font-family: &quot;Futura Sd&quot;, Futura, &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 158, 224);">
          Pourquoi cet audit ?
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm" style="color:#696969;">
          60% des PME ayant subi une cyberattaque deposent le bilan sous 6 mois. Nos tests simulent de vraies attaques : phishing, ransomware, intrusion réseau. Vous recevez un rapport clair avec les failles detectees et les correctifs a appliquer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border p-6 bg-white/85" style="border-color: rgba(0, 158, 224, 0.3);">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="font-family: &quot;Futura Sd&quot;, Futura, &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 158, 224);">Ce que comprend l'audit</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color:#696969;">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: rgb(217, 224, 33);"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>
            Analyse de votre parc informatique (jusqu'a 30 IP/VLAN)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: rgb(217, 224, 33);"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>
            Test d'intrusion automatise par IA (partenaire SXIPHER)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: rgb(217, 224, 33);"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>
            Rapport de vulnerabilites et plan d'action priorise
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: rgb(217, 224, 33);"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>
            Conformité RGPD et NIS2 incluse
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="italic text-base" style="color:#696969;">
        « L'audit a revele deux breches critiques. Bugzero a corrige le tout en une semaine. »
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold" style="color: rgb(0, 158, 224);">PME a Monaco</p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5" style="background-color:#009EE0;">
          Protégéz votre activite des maintenant
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <fragment slot="footer">
    <Footer />
  </fragment>
</Layout>